Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:37.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:49.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:55.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:01:03.25,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:07.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:22.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:27.69,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:34.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:41.58,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:37.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:49.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:55.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:01:03.25,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:07.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:22.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:27.69,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:34.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:41.58,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:56.13,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(489,384)}Episode 9 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I really don't understand how I was the one to suggest it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez! He's already getting naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to say something like "let's stop here" now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's embarrassing, so turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't make a fuss about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't taken anything off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take everything off one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, instead... you undress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I said something as stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as telling him to take off my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't know what to do, or what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... I don't know where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it like you're at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the sandy dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in swimming trunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why don't you change into your bikini, Nana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared, we can stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make you regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, I want to do something that will make us both happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't just want your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like you're pushing yourself even a little, then it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... I'm not making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... even I'm starting to get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so even guys get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... without holding back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will let you give yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My Japanese is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it hurts, please raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a dentist or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't regret this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Dad... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone I want to devote everything to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the one precious to me, who's difficult to replace...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with anything else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encountering him must have been destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if anyone says differently, I won't believe in destiny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even despite that, I wonder if I've been dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's just been so much fortune... beauty... fascination...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the reality seems so dreamlike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this all just a dream that seems so realistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why's he wearing a happi coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy dream? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He was talking about something else when he wore the happi coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words they say at weddings sure are nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Christmas present... give me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is this reali--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's reality! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this sorta hurts, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right hand, right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. Sorry, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stick with it for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something else right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... like you're cramming your mouth full of those steamed meat buns you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something full of happiness like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Get dressed! Get dressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our study stuff is downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it with me, so sneak out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She must've seen my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never show my face in front of your mom ever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't something else be bugging you more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, her coming home was the worst punch line ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it funny? Like, really funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just so like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. Did I hurt your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Yano, you're dressed pretty lightly, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be disappointed, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I made such a huge thing out of it, and now I look completely uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, didn't it feel like a play, with all of those overdramatic lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be a theatre? Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel embarrassed about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I was moved by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad the person I love is Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no chance that we'll make this an anniversary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For our first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even enter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I think you know that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No penetration. No nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we head back, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will things be okay with your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd the old hag have to come home at a time like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My house is no good at all! Totally out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Up until now, I've just thought of sex as a sport!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But I was wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sex is something sacred."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, he came over to my place and said that with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have a loose screw or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Is he really that into his current girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he have sex with Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that her name? What's she like? I've never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I saw them walking and holding hands once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she's kind of round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Round?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so normal that you'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't it fine the way it is, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means he's starting to heal from what happened with Nana-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, the one left behind just has to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do more than just that. You should have the time of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your finest sake, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, he had a couple screws loose when he was going out with Nana-san too, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only 8,000 yen. A special bargain, just for you! But you have to pay up-front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little expensive. You sure you're not overcharging?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought them for 14,000 yen, and they're practically right out of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not expensive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you worn them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe two or three times?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying. They're dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean them off with an eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have more stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw in a cap and this one-of-a-kind secret figure as a special service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 yen altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're raising the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.92,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to buy so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.46,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano came to sell today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.97,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the shoes alone, 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3,250.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3,500. I won't go any higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even pay for a hotel room with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get him. He's at the end of his rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were selling your One Stars, I wouldn't mind paying 8,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he stare at my feet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you. I'm not selling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8,000 yen's too cheap in the first place, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll pay for them using my Internet account.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the cash right now. I'm in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yano-kun. I'll buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? You're so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cruel, cold world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I think you're the cruel one here, no matter how I look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had my hair just right, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you had it just right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all fall apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a marimo youkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a marimo youkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He smells good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... there's some strange rumors going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you've become a miser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.25,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}Sign: A miser ~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saving up for a hotel room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... my house is just too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know when my parents will be out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done a lot of thinking about it too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... kinda think that love hotels...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are not really what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're right, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd prefer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.70,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we kinda rushed the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was thinking I really want to make it something special in the right situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going out of your way, I'd like to go somewhere like hot springs or the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way it'll become a memory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll... become a... memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel fee... the train fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it were Tokyo Disneyland, it would be even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How much would that all cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both save up, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might take some time, but I'm sure we'll double the happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll save up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll really both save up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gamble on Takahashi's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll take about half a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's really okay with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably have enough in time for our graduation class trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the newest issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the happiness I feel right now once belonged to someone else long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sorta feel like I'm being gypped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much have you saved so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs36}721 {\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the fireworks this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the festival, the Kiri Festival, and the beach, all together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's create a ton of memories together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like the word "memory".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason. In my Japanese class in elementary school, I read a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story called "What Color Was That Girl's Dress?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls, named A and B are recalling an old story together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get into this discussion about a picture hanging on the wall of one of the staircase landings in their elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture of a girl picking flowers in front of a deep red sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really never read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A says, "Oh! How nostalgic. You're talking about the picture of the girl in a pretty yellow dress, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then B says, "No, the dress she was wearing was red, just like the sunset!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, it was red!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, it was definitely yellow."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alright, then why don't we go see for ourselves?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them, filled with excitement, reached the old, nostalgic school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What color was that girl's dress?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't have a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a black and white picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dress that dark silhouette wore was scribbled completely black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:21:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet in their memories, both bickering girls were sure that the dress in the picture had a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Human memories are too vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking something has color when it doesn't, making things more dramatic than they really are, glorifying things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives new, greater meaning than was actually there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't believe any of this talk about "beautiful memories".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you believe in, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's right in front of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, wanna come shopping with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I dropped her stuff all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get really mad at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a copy of this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yamamoto-san also reads poetry books...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though she's always reading all that hard stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, hurry up and give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't notice we dropped it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What am I gonna do? I took it as soon as I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a little younger, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's Yano, and to his left, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... this is probably... Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Yamamoto-san have...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:43.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu ga sukoshi ugoita ki ga suru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.41,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hizashi mo mijikaku itsukazurete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:24:00.83,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Futari no basu ha kawaranai machi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:08.09,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashitteiru koto hotto shiteta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:16.97,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mado no soto itsumo mitai ni miteru anata
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:25.40,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Soshite watashi mo mane wo shiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.24,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumo mitai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:37.74,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari ha onaji nano ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:45.75,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikitai basho ha? Damatteitatte iinda yo ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:54.59,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee futari ha onaji nano ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:25:04.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshii kimochi... Anata no shisen ha ima, mienakute....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:43.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the seasons have changed slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:52.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sunbeams have thinned and will one day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:24:00.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was relieved, knowing our bus
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:08.09,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,was riding through our unchanged city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:16.97,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You always gaze up to me from outside my window
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:25.40,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I mimic you by doing the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.24,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:37.74,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we're both the same?
